Utility-Scripts
---------------

This is a collection of useful scripts written in everything from
Batch, PowerShell, Python, and anything else.


Included Scripts
----------------

wsus.bat - A Windows Server Update Services Switcher
	A simple batch file that will quickly and easily flip a non-domain
	system to use a local WSUS server for Windows updates.

Trust-Relationship-Fixer - Automated domain leave/join scripts
	A collection of scripts that will automatically leave a domain, and then
	rejoin the domain. Used to fix trust relationship issues when using system
	restore and a computer forgets its domain password.

manage-printers.ps1 - A PowerShell printer management script
	A not-quite-completed printer script written in PowerShell. Supposed to easily
	add, remove, and replace printers on a local system.